{"tid":2060681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Twitter宣布刪除17萬個親中網軍帳戶","createTime":"2020-06-11T23:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T18:17:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":885,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7206795b5bbba1b67d547b666c872559de66ae","tid":2060681,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195327&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0n8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=edac66f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195327&h=d2d0670a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195327</a><br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，推特（Twitter）週四宣布，已關閉跟中國政府有關的170000個帳戶，與推特合作的專家檢視這些帳戶，稱他們對香港抗爭、武漢肺炎等主題發表欺騙性的論述。推特表示，這些帳戶發表親中共言論，因違反平台規則被刪除。與推特合作的澳洲戰略政策研究機構表示，這些帳戶目的在於擴大中共影響力。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，推特表示已辨識出23750個帳戶為高度參與的核心網路，共發表348608則推文，多為親北京內容，另外有150000個帳戶則利用轉發的方式擴大這些言論&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;"},{"pid":"c58443b8e71f570e7171bc099bf0efdd96add30f","tid":2060681,"uid":273703,"like":267,"dislike":2,"score":265,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:55:17.000Z","msg":"之前屌中共屌到 ban 左我又開返未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037658dd0171a52be5ddbd072994edf929219aac","tid":2060681,"uid":29093,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:55:20.000Z","msg":"twitter 170K<br />\n<br />\n連登當有 5%    都 8.5K <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔出奇"},{"pid":"68a42bb6552bf1c28cefb77501bf1714f46047df","tid":2060681,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:55:30.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/fa